  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/06c30ca802c45d88d0b47d1781f4fb39.avif?t=1723787893\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><strong>Galaxy Too Far</strong> gives you control over AI system. The main goal is to be useful for your Creator and you finally found a good planet to make it a resource base.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/928837128b338ac968e9f756170728dd.avif?t=1723787893\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br>Start your expansion with the most basic structures. Use the mining system to extract resources. Perform primary processing, and then create your first technological materials. While drones help you to transfer fragile materials, pipelines move heavy raw resources.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/e91b7ab0d2a30081ae2e38ead1564bb4.avif?t=1723787893\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br>Start investigating energy resources available on the alien planet. From classic wind and solar energy to geothermal and cosmic radiation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/10f3e95b4854c990c3308a3a252fff64.avif?t=1723787893\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br>Terrain based gameplay. Ground level, biome type, water level matter.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/6879116bc33bb9b8fb73127261c3b4fd.avif?t=1723787893\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br>Complex Augmentation system. Helps you to determine where you can build a specific building, how it will be connected to other systems. Where underground resource is located, what temperature is in the hovering building spot and more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/413c6b4d43383d16aac9d44bea510a6b.avif?t=1723787893\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br>Close the ring around the planet and prepare the Beacon for a final strike. It will require a lot of resources and energy to accomplish. Use orbital constructions to support your planet infrastructure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/04e214b1368d6c17f2094d4c7b0d924a.avif?t=1723787893\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br>Terraform the planet. Create your own way to build, collect and harvest.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/06c30ca802c45d88d0b47d1781f4fb39.avif?t=1723787893\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><strong>Galaxy Too Far</strong> gives you control over AI system. The main goal is to be useful for your Creator and you finally found a good planet to make it a resource base.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/928837128b338ac968e9f756170728dd.avif?t=1723787893\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br>Start your expansion with the most basic structures. Use the mining system to extract resources. Perform primary processing, and then create your first technological materials. While drones help you to transfer fragile materials, pipelines move heavy raw resources.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/e91b7ab0d2a30081ae2e38ead1564bb4.avif?t=1723787893\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br>Start investigating energy resources available on the alien planet. From classic wind and solar energy to geothermal and cosmic radiation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/10f3e95b4854c990c3308a3a252fff64.avif?t=1723787893\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br>Terrain based gameplay. Ground level, biome type, water level matter.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/6879116bc33bb9b8fb73127261c3b4fd.avif?t=1723787893\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br>Complex Augmentation system. Helps you to determine where you can build a specific building, how it will be connected to other systems. Where underground resource is located, what temperature is in the hovering building spot and more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/413c6b4d43383d16aac9d44bea510a6b.avif?t=1723787893\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br>Close the ring around the planet and prepare the Beacon for a final strike. It will require a lot of resources and energy to accomplish. Use orbital constructions to support your planet infrastructure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/04e214b1368d6c17f2094d4c7b0d924a.avif?t=1723787893\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br>Terraform the planet. Create your own way to build, collect and harvest.",
